    <div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Settings Coming Soon</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        This is a placeholder page. Settings functionality will be implemented in future updates.
        Contact your system administrator if you need to modify any system configurations.
      </p>
